txt.en: You have turned in a stack of trophies for a modest reward suitable for a collector such as yourself.
Wanted: Blackened sword sheaths from the Dead in the Barrow-downs. Deliver the items to Second-watcher Heathstraw at the Boar Fountain in Bree.
'These reek of death. Thank you for disposing of the wights.'
'There are wights wandering the Barrow-downs, they say.'
Men of Bree Task: Blackened Sword Sheaths
Second-watcher Heathstraw is offering compensation for the collection of blackened sword sheaths from the Dead found in the Barrow-downs.
Deliver the blackened sword sheaths to Second-watcher Heathstraw
You have been tasked with finding blackened sword sheaths from the Dead in the Barrow-downs. Second-watcher Heathstraw awaits the delivery of these items at the Boar Fountain in Bree.
Wanted: Blackened sword sheaths from the Dead in the Barrow-downs.
